We are constantly in danger

5
00:00:09.375 --> 00:00:10.916
Our lands are coveted by

6
00:00:11.000 --> 00:00:12.541
neighboring usurpers

7
00:00:12.666 --> 00:00:14.208
You know who I'm talking about

8
00:00:14.375 --> 00:00:16.166
Immigrants, culture inundators

9
00:00:16.458 --> 00:00:18.500
They want to wipe us off the face of the Earth

10
