They want our land for themselves

11
00:00:23.041 --> 00:00:25.083
Our survival is in our hands

12
00:00:25.458 --> 00:00:27.500
and we are ready to fight, damn it!

13
00:00:28.583 --> 00:00:30.625
The most crucial war for Estonian history begins!

14
00:00:31.083 --> 00:00:33.375
We declare Estonia a sanctuary

15
00:00:33.958 --> 00:00:35.666
We may be small, but

16
00:00:35.875 --> 00:00:37.583
our spirit soars to the sky

17
00:00:38.000 --> 00:00:40.541
To be Estonian is proud and noble, resist!

18
00:00:41.083 --> 00:00:44.500
Our garden is small, and the soil is thin

19
00:00:44.875 --> 00:00:47.166
and if we want to reap from it, then

20
00:00:47.458 --> 00:00:49.750
